   <concept id="FAR_1_304" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">1.304</ph> Agency control and compliance procedures.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d34e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d36e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Under the authorities of <xref href="1.301.dita#FAR_1_301"
                        base="i1126703"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">1.301</xref>(d), agencies shall control and limit issuance of agency acquisition regulations and, in particular, local agency directives that restrain the flexibilities found in the FAR, and shall establish formal procedures for the review of these documents to assure compliance with this <xref href="Part_1.dita#FAR_Part_1"
                        base="i1129394"
                        outputclass="fm:Part"
                        class="- topic/xref ">part  1</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d36e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            Agency acquisition regulations shall not-</p>
               <ol id="d34e38" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d36e27">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                Unnecessarily repeat, paraphrase, or otherwise restate material contained in the FAR or higher-level agency acquisition regulations; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d36e32">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                Except as required by law or as provided in <xref href="Subpart_1.4.dita#FAR_Subpart_1_4"
                              base="i1126600"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  1.4</xref>, conflict or be inconsistent with FAR content.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d36e40">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            Agencies shall evaluate all regulatory coverage in agency acquisition regulations to determine if it could apply to other agencies. Coverage that is not peculiar to one agency shall be recommended for inclusion in the FAR.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
